1129	    /// C: portion of `lua_settop` (lapi.c) — `L->top.p = newtop` plus the
1130	    /// `for (; diff > 0; diff--) setnilvalue(s2v(L->top.p++))` clear loop.
1131	    /// PORT NOTE: callers pass an absolute `StackIdx` (e.g. `top + 1`,
